# Proxmox

Proxmox:
Proxmox is a virtualization software that runs virtual appliances and virtual machines.

You can download proxmox from this location:
http://www.proxmox.com/downloads/proxmox-ve/17-iso-imaProxmox

You can manage everything in proxmox from your web browser.

Proxmox can be accessed at port 8006.

Just take it on a browser: IP_address:8006

Login username is root and the password is what you enter during installation.

The ability to use OpenVZ along with KVM on the same server make proxmox unique.. Proxmox is easily clusterable and we can easily migrate the boxes as well as do centralized management of the cluster.
